### Phase 6 — Jinja-Based Report Generator
Prevent LLM formatting hallucinations by rewriting the Report Agent to compile structured states into Markdown using a standardized Jinja template.

#### [NEW] [report_template.md](file:///c:/Users/ankit/Desktop/AutoBug/backend/app/templates/report_template.md)
* Design a modular Jinja template rendering:
  - Facts vs AI Conclusions sections.
  - Performance Complexity table (before/after).
  - Validation & reproduction logs.
  - Dynamic execution metrics (phase duration, costs).

#### [MODIFY] [report_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/ankit/Desktop/AutoBug/backend/app/agents/report_agent.py)
* Replace raw LLM report compilation with a Jinja context render using the pipeline structured state.

