### Phase 10 — Pipeline Consistency Checker
Establish a final rule-based checker node before publishing pull requests or saving issues.

#### [NEW] [consistency_checker.py](file:///c:/Users/ankit/Desktop/AutoBug/backend/app/agents/consistency_checker.py)
* Add verification rules:
  - If tests failed → Reviewer approved must be `False`.
  - If confidence > 90% → Tests must have passed.
  - If reproduction occurred → Evidence logs must be present.

